        net.sergeych.tools.Binder getParams()
        Represent query as Binder of key-values. Values should be decoded, either String or BasicHTTPService.FileUpload. Contains both query parameters from URL arguments and from forms, where present. Each key is a String; a value is either a single String or List of String, depending on how many values were provided for the single key.
        Returns:
